John D. NAGLE, as Commissioner of Immigration for the Port of San Francisco, California, Appellant, v. LUM YIN KIN, Appellee. No. 6380. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 17, 1931.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
